snippet.title: [c64] Black Hawk (1984)
snippet.description:
I had completely forgotten this and stumbled upon it by accident. This is not a very good run and I made further before. This one chopper fired a bullet which followed my plane and was impossible to dodge. Hadn't noticed about those following bullets before. I read something about 99 levels. There's always some new stuff coming in every mission at least in the beginning of the game.

Music is Wagner's Valkyrie.

Published by Creative Sparks

http://www.lemon64.com/games/details.php?ID=283
